    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "TRANSLATION FROM SPANISH",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Valparaiso, March 4, 1953",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Director of the Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Washington",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "United States, North America",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Subject: Individual who may possibly be connected with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "In writing to you who directs the influential Office of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Investigation which has international connections, I would like to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "state the following:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "1°-a) I had the opportunity to read in a \"Chilean\" police magazine, in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "the section entitled \"Perfect Escapes,\" the escape of Dr. LINKE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "(42 years old, widower, who sometime in 1950, in London, was arrested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "on the 8th floor of the Building of Departments (?). The reason for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "his detention was his possible collaboration with VLADIMIR VLASAV in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "\"divulging to foreign governments English aviation secrets\".)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "In his attempt to get away, which occurred between 4 and 5",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "in the morning, a strange thing happened, \"when the police came near",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "the 8th floor, the whole building became dark, the elevators stopped",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "and the telephones and loudspeakers became silent. When the police",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "arrived on the 8th floor with their flash lights, they immediately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "went off. (Nevertheless, he was arrested at 6 A.M.).",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "b) Dr. LINKE escaped from the Kent Prison (a few days after",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "he was imprisoned) and according to statements of the author of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "article, which should be accurate, he did it in the following manner:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Between 12 midnight and 2 A.M., in rainy weather, Dr. JULIUS LINKE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "disappeared under the following circumstances: the electricity, elevators,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "telephones, and flash lights of the guards would not function.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
